Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.09,0:00:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, make way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.22,0:00:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get in the way of the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.38,0:00:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.97,0:00:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,At least tell us\Nthe police's thoughts on the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.76,0:00:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think this is another incident\Ncaused by that serial killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The murdered Jopp couple\Ndon't have kids either, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.69,0:00:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how you look at it,\Nthis case is exactly like
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.82,0:00:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the serial murders of middle-aged couples\Nhappening all across Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.19,0:00:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.32,0:00:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that an investigator\Nfrom the BKA is coming too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.70,0:00:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So this must be connected\Nto the serial murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.91,0:00:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.29,0:00:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.79,0:00:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be faster to just ask\Nthe BKA investigator directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.13,0:00:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.80,0:00:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise I'll outwit the other papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.84,0:00:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Save a big headline space for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.60,0:00:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.23,0:00:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.81,0:01:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Kipper from the Hamburg Tag.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.11,0:01:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the BKA investigator, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.11,0:01:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like a comment from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.15,0:01:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The relationship between this case\Nand the middle-aged couple serial murders…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.78,0:01:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kipper from the Hamburg Talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.70,0:01:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is some special information\Njust for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.29,0:01:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.83,0:01:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This case is one of\Nthe middle-aged couple serial murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.75,0:01:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.05,0:01:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Then is the suspect that Japanese doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.47,0:01:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I just saw the report.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.26,0:01:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same modus operandi\Nas the serial murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.22,0:01:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the exclusive news. Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.02,0:01:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hold it.\N-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.52,0:01:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hamburg Tag is\Na leading newspaper here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So, your article will be run\Nin leading newspapers all over Germany?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.74,0:01:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.55,0:03:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.51,0:03:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I have now become the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I knock?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.77,0:03:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's best that the Jopp couple\Nnot be cautious around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.36,0:03:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, looks like an amiable couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.03,0:03:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They easily invite me in\Nand let me into the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.78,0:04:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They are not cautious in the slightest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.25,0:04:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The husband's chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I sit in the seat for guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.76,0:04:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In a few minutes, the husband will\Nbe dead on the floor over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I have not yet taken action.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she is not in this living room yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She is making tea in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.69,0:04:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Before she can serve the tea,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.53,0:04:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,she is stabbed from behind in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.53,0:04:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That means I must\Nbegin taking action soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.87,0:04:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I take my knife out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The husband hurriedly tries to stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A single stab.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.08,0:04:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops, I made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The husband runs away\Nwith an injured left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.88,0:04:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My next attack is to his right shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.72,0:04:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Another dumb mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm acting like a complete amateur.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The husband is calling out to his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But the wife in the kitchen\Ncannot hear him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.48,0:05:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She is hard of hearing lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Make noise. Scream and cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I can end your wife after killing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.28,0:05:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He's cornered.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.86,0:05:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A mark from his left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I've cornered the husband\Nin front of this sideboard. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.79,0:05:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The final blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, even now,\NI haven't dealt the final blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The husband dies on the floor\Nfive meters from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I not deal the final blow here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.98,0:05:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.44,0:05:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the man\Nwho killed the Jopp couple?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.57,0:06:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not necessarily the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.28,0:06:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just asking a small favor\Nof the local residents here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If this man appears,\Ntreat him very normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.62,0:06:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, contact me promptly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all I ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.13,0:06:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.46,0:06:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You will not be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.09,0:06:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I guarantee it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it is surprising\Nsuch a nasty incident
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.68,0:06:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,happened in a quiet housing district\Nlike this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Truly, the Jopp couple\Nwere such good people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.06,0:06:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,When I called out to her every morning,\Nthe wife always greeted me so cheerfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You called out to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The wife was hard of hearing\Nsince roughly a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What? That can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It was on the chart\Nfrom the family doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.37,0:06:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She would've barely heard your greetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, knowing Mrs. Jopp,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.25,0:06:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,she must've sensed I was there\Nand greeted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.92,0:07:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The people in this neighborhood\Ndon't know she is hard of hearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.72,0:07:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, what an incredible company.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.35,0:07:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Advancing this far at this young age
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,is no normal feat, Mr. Ziebel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the auto manufacturer we signed\Na contract with just happened to do well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.24,0:07:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to give you my condolences\Nfor the death of your aunt and uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.57,0:07:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, my aunt and uncle\Nwere the only relatives I had left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The couple had no children,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,so they must have doted\Na lot on you, their nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.59,0:07:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, as if I were their real son.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you'll catch the culprit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.18,0:07:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.22,0:07:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be\Nthe former Japanese doctor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.31,0:07:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quite well-informed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.06,0:07:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:07:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,as there were incidents\Nsimilar to this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.15,0:08:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How much will your inheritance be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.57,0:08:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.82,0:08:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, since Mr. Jopp\Nwas such a wealthy person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.41,0:08:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that somehow relevant to this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.16,0:08:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose the only heir to their estate
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.25,0:08:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.88,0:08:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That talk is not appropriate\Nat a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.80,0:08:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if a company is boasting\Ngreat achievements on the outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,on the inside,\Nits financial situation may be desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.89,0:08:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a thing is quite common.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.77,0:08:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like you're insinuating\NI killed them for the inheritance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.44,0:08:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the perfect alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You have witnesses that say
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you took your secretary and workers\Nto dinner after a business meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.62,0:08:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:08:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.21,0:09:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Lunge!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.42,0:09:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.34,0:09:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Of what exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.55,0:09:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.68,0:09:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,These past few days,\NI've been looking into their nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.39,0:09:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,His company is excellent at a glance,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but internal conditions are strained\Ndue to failed investments and stocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.23,0:09:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And you've thoroughly looked into\Nthe nephew's company's vicinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What is really going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think this case is linked\Nto the middle-aged couple serial murders?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.03,0:09:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The other papers are taking\Nthe same stance after our exclusive scoop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If it is irrelevant to the serial murders,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.50,0:09:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that's grave misinformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're exactly right. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.84,0:09:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the work of a copycat
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,pretending to be\Npart of the serial murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.59,0:09:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to change the article right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.05,0:09:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-No, it's fine the way it is now.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.47,0:10:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The article will say it is one\Nof the middle-aged couple serial murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.23,0:10:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.94,0:10:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I write such lies--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.36,0:10:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Just write it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite how this seems,\NI'm an unimportant journalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.82,0:10:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Pressuring me will do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.45,0:10:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name was Kipper, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.87,0:10:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful lady you have there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A warm household.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You have such a wonderful wife\Nand daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.25,0:10:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's only natural you'd want to commit\Nadultery with such a beautiful lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.14,0:10:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it as is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No, a special report focusing even more\Non the middle-aged couple murders is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.60,0:10:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That will draw him out for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.74,0:10:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They were such a wonderful couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.51,0:11:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.76,0:11:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, have you heard anything about\Nthem having a foster child?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Even for a short while, 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,have you seen them living with\Nan unfamiliar child?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.60,0:11:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.81,0:11:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That couple was\Nvery affectionate toward their nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.69,0:11:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, would you like another cup of tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.36,0:11:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.99,0:11:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no mistaking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the man from the photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.46,0:11:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He is at my house now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.96,0:11:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.97,0:11:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Lunge,\Nsomeone is here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.39,0:11:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the nephew of\Nthe murdered Jopp couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you think I'm the culprit, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.73,0:12:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think I killed two people\Nfor an inheritance, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that I'm in a lot of debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.95,0:12:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The fortune they left me
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.66,0:12:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,will probably save me\Nfrom this pinch I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.37,0:12:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I'm not that kind of person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You visited me over something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.13,0:12:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"Something like that"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.38,0:12:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?\NYou treated me like a culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.34,0:12:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I have somewhere I must go to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.64,0:12:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.60,0:12:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to take back\Nthe rude things you said before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.48,0:12:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The police are no longer\Nchasing after your tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.02,0:12:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The police here have deemed you innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.53,0:12:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that enough for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.57,0:13:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Then who do you think\Nis the culprit of this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.16,0:13:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The culprit of this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.83,0:13:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I can arrest that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's a bloodstain there…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.77,0:13:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He messed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.48,0:13:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.77,0:13:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you think this case wasn't a crime\Ncommitted by that Japanese doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.27,0:13:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what you'd call a copycat crime of\Nthe middle-aged couple serial murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.33,0:13:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There was something in this case\Nthat wasn't in the serial murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.21,0:13:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The culprit cornered the victim here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But instead of here,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:14:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,he dealt the final blow over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.76,0:14:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did he hesitate for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.73,0:14:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There's emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.27,0:14:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Emotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.23,0:14:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In the crimes committed\Nby the man I am chasing,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.57,0:14:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,the crime scenes\Nare presented like robberies,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.53,0:14:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but you can't feel any emotion from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.33,0:14:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But the crime scene this time
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.04,0:14:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,is overflowing with emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.96,0:14:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Just by having his and his victim's face\Nreflected in the mirror,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,he becomes flustered.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.51,0:14:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, rest at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The police here are incompetent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.52,0:14:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how I look at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the work of a copycat\Nimitating Johan's murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:14:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How long will this continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.57,0:15:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How long?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.37,0:15:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.33,0:15:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally meet, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.72,0:15:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been searching for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A very long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to have a long talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.48,0:15:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no use in running now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a nice chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How long do you plan\Nto repeat this cycle, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.51,0:16:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If only it weren't for you…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.73,0:16:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Get off of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.03,0:16:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It was me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.24,0:16:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed the Jopp couple!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.15,0:16:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll turn myself in! Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.62,0:16:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no interest in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.58,0:16:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this wound?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate,\Nhe'll die from excessive bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.49,0:17:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did this to Inspector Lunge?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.83,0:17:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to leave him\Nin front of a hospital and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.59,0:17:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.64,0:17:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.85,0:17:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the key to the handcuffs?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.94,0:17:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother looking for your gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm holding on to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, hurry and give me\Nthe key to the handcuffs!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.28,0:17:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do anything like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.20,0:17:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw your wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.03,0:17:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Luckily, it hasn't reached\Nyour abdominal cavity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.58,0:17:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you're losing a lot of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.62,0:17:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll die if it doesn't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.59,0:18:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Confess your crimes, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.84,0:18:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.43,0:18:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The director and two doctors\Nmurdered at Eisler Memorial Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The middle-aged couple serial murders\Nfor the past three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.85,0:18:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Confess that all of these are your crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.56,0:18:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll really die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.82,0:18:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Was this all the work of "Johan"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.24,0:18:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're searching for Johan,\Nthe real culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no Johan in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You yourself are Johan, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.33,0:18:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Confess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There was nothing decent\Nin this abandoned warehouse,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.96,0:18:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but I did find what I need\Nfor first-aid treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.84,0:18:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I need my hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If my hands are free, I can save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You were an outstanding doctor\Nwhen you were Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.14,0:19:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to act like a flawless saint, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How many did you kill with those hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.81,0:19:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You are wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,When will you change to Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.07,0:19:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,When will your good person persona\Nflip to that of a cold-blooded murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.29,0:19:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I am never wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,With your blood pressure going down,\Nyour consciousness is getting hazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.46,0:19:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,At your crime scenes…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.92,0:19:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't talk anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.26,0:19:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Your crime scenes show no emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.55,0:19:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.26,0:19:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,When you handle the life and death\Nof people every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.39,0:19:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,emotions disappear, huh, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.14,0:19:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That cool composure\Nis always at the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.57,0:19:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You are truly composed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.86,0:19:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.70,0:20:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I had doubts with every surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I make a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.00,0:20:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I finish the job well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.46,0:20:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Will any unforeseen trouble occur?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I was actually trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.71,0:20:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A person's life was in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,In my hands…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.39,0:20:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I possibly stay composed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.81,0:20:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.90,0:20:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.98,0:20:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stop your bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.52,0:20:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the key?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it in your pants pocket?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.95,0:20:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll shoot…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.92,0:20:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.55,0:21:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.80,0:21:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You look healthier\Nthan when you're at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.64,0:21:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for worrying about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.81,0:21:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, the first-aid treatment\Nwas done perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.94,0:21:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctor said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.27,0:21:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He said you'd be dead by now\Nif it weren't for such correct treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.82,0:21:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So that means I owe Tenma my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.82,0:21:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Tenma did escape,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.16,0:21:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,but Ziebel confessed\Nto the Jopp couple murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.37,0:21:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You did great work, Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.33,0:21:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.42,0:21:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-What do you think?\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.88,0:21:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma saved Lunge's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.84,0:21:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That might interfere with Tenma's arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.43,0:21:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we remove Lunge\Nfrom the Tenma case?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.10,0:21:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.52,0:21:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for all the trouble\NInspector Lunge is giving you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.69,0:21:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no trouble at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He gives a nice impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.32,0:21:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We've told him he doesn't have to\Nrush his rehabilitation so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.32,0:22:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but he's already gripping the ball\Nand walking down the hallways.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.32,0:22:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems to be having a very fun time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.41,0:22:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.91,0:22:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he says all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.58,0:22:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,that nothing is more fun than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.54,0:22:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that culprit's name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.09,0:22:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.71,0:22:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He said nothing is more fun\Nthan chasing after a culprit like Tenma.
